<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - USCS raised to buy.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - USCS raised to buy.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Merrill Lynch said it upgraded USCS International Inc to near-term buy from accumulate and named the company its Focus One Stock of the Week.</p>
<p>-- Kept long-term buy rating.</p>
<p>-- Shares rose 2-1/2 to 29.</p>
<p>((-- Wall Street desk, 212 859-1730))</p>
